pullRequest.body:
Show that max nilpotent ideal <= radical for Lie algebras
---
This PR establishes that the max nilpotent ideal is contained in the radical for Lie algebras.
A somewhat similar result is already presented in Nilpotent.lean, where it is shown that the center is contained in the max nilpotent ideal for Lie algebras.

This work is part of the framework:
https://github.com/orgs/leanprover-community/projects/17
